About this item

  • Liquid I.V. Hydration Multiplier – Helps you hydrate 2x faster than water alone with Hydration Multiplier, a great-tasting electrolyte drink powder with five essential vitamins and 3x the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks. Whether you’re in need of hydration for exercise, travel, or long nights, Liquid I.V. Hydration Multiplier packets have you covered.
  • Great taste -Lemon Lime Hydration Multiplier is the flavor that started it all. This sunny mix of citrus flavors is equal parts zesty and refreshing. An instant fan favorite.
  • Cellular Transport Technology – The science of Cellular Transport Technology (CTT), used in Liquid I.V. products, is based on an optimal ratio of ingredients designed to enhance rapid absorption of water and other key ingredients into your body. Thanks to this fast acting system, Hydration Multiplier helps provide faster, more efficient hydration.
  • Non-GMO and made with premium ingredients – Hydration Multiplier Electrolyte Powder Drink Mix is made with natural flavors and has no artificial colors or sweeteners. Every serving contains 5 essential vitamins: vitamins B3, B5, B6, B12 and vitamin C. It's also gluten-free, soy-free, and dairy-free.
  • On-the-go hydration – Enjoy convenient, on-the-go hydration with Hydration Multiplier. These single-serving, travel-friendly stick packets are perfect for taking to the gym, sports games, and long flights. Pour one easy-to-open stick packet into 16oz of water, mix or shake, and hydrate.
  • Global impact – Liquid I.V. believes equitable access to clean and abundant water is the foundation of a healthier world. We prioritize partnerships with leading water, humanitarian, and community-based organizations to fund and foster innovative solutions to help communities protect both their water and their futures.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Liquid IV vs. TruWILD Hydrate Comparison Review
I've been an avid consumer of hydration products for years, and the two brands that have caught my attention recently are Liquid IV and the relatively new player on the block, Truwild Hydrate. Both have their merits, but let me tell you why I've become a dedicated fan of Truwild.Liquid IV:Liquid IV has been the go-to choice for many when it comes to hydration. It's easily available, widely recognized, and it gets the job done. However, there are a couple of factors that have started to make me look for alternatives.Truwild Hydrate:Truwild is a fresh face in the hydration game, but it's quickly making waves. What sets Truwild apart is its commitment to providing a natural, sugar-free alternative. Unlike Liquid IV, which contains added sugars, Truwild opts for a more health-conscious approach, making it suitable for those watching their sugar intake.One standout feature of Truwild Hydrate is its dedication to using only natural ingredients. As someone who values clean and wholesome nutrition, I appreciate that Truwild doesn't rely on artificial additives or synthetic flavors. It's a refreshing change from the overly processed options on the market.Another aspect that won me over is the fact that Truwild is not owned by a massive conglomerate. This means they have the flexibility to prioritize quality over mass production. Truwild is made in small batches, ensuring that every packet is crafted with care and attention to detail. This is in stark contrast to Liquid IV, which, due to its scale, may not always maintain the same level of quality control.Both products do a commendable job at keeping you hydrated, but Truwild has managed to edge ahead in my book. It's a conscious choice for those looking to reduce their sugar intake and opt for more natural, quality ingredients. Plus, supporting a smaller, independent brand like Truwild feels like a step in the right direction.In conclusion, while Liquid IV has been a solid option for hydration for years, Truwild Hydrate has won me over with its commitment to health-conscious ingredients, small-batch production, and the absence of added sugars. If you're seeking a better alternative, I highly recommend giving Truwild a try. It's the refreshing change the hydration market needed.

The packaging is sleek and portable, making it easy to toss into my bag or keep in my car. I appreciate the individual serving packets – it's so convenient for travel or when I'm on the move.

Overall, Liquid IV Lemon Lime Hydration Mix is a must-have in my daily routine. It's become my go-to solution for staying hydrated and feeling my best. If you're looking for a delicious, effective, and convenient way to up your hydration game, look no further – this product is a five-star winner!
